IRS990.ActivityOrMissionDesc: TO PROMOTE AMATEUR WRESTLING IN ITS MANY FORMS TO CALIFORNIANS OF ALL AGES. TO ENDEAVOR TO EDUCATE THE CA PUBLIC IN WRESTLING STYLES, MAKE WRESTLING FUN & EXCITING, PROVIDE PLANNED ACTIVITIES, AND IMPROVE THE QUALITY OF CALIFORNIA WRESTLING AT THE COMPETITIVE LEVEL.
IRS990.MissionDesc: TO PROMOTE AMATEUR WRESTLING IN ITS MANY FORMS TO CALIFORNIANS OF ALL AGES. TO ENDEAVOR TO EDUCATE THE CA PUBLIC IN WRESTLING STYLES, MAKE WRESTLING FUN & EXCITING, PROVIDE PLANNED ACTIVITIES, AND IMPROVE THE QUALITY OF CALIFORNIA WRESTLING AT THE COMPETITIVE LEVEL.
IRS990.Desc: CALIFORNIA USA WRESTLING IS THE NATIONAL GOVERNING BODY FOR THE SPORT OF WRESTLING IN THE STATE OF CA AND ITS REPRESENTATIVE TO USA WRESTLING. CALIFORNIA USA WRESTLING HAS MORE THAN 19,801 MEMBERS THAT INCLUDE ATHLETES OF ALL AGES, COACHES, OFFICIALS, PARENTS AND FANS STRIVING TO STRENGTHEN THE SPORT. EACH YEAR, CALIFORNIA USA WRESTLING CHARTERS OVER 564 WRESTLING CLUBS AND SANCTIONS OVER 177 LOCAL AND STATE COMPETITIONS.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: Form 990, Part VI, Section A, Line 6
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: ANY PERSON WHO DESIRES TO PROMOTE CALIFORNIA WRESTLING EITHER THROUGH ACTION, WORD OR DEED QUALIFIES FOR MEMBERSHIP. THERE ARE FIVE CLASSES OF MEMBERSHIP - COMPETITIVE MEMBERSHIP, COACHES MEMBERSHIP, OFFICAL MEMBERSHIP, GENERAL MEMBERSHIP, CLUB MEMBERSHIP AND PARTNER MEMBERSHIP.
